Vamprah/wheeljack:

"Well" said Wheeljack "What do you think about the desing?"


Vamprah couldn't speak, she was surpriced with her new look: she was 
a feathered helmet, her wings was covered with feathers, and she had 
alot Owl-like characteristics.

But other thinks caught her attention: her mettalic gray skin was now 
more pale; her golden eyes were pale blue; Her lips were thin... She 
didn't seemed a dangerous Predacon...  She seemed, in a word, a 
MAximal.

"Well"said again Wheeljack "What do you think?"

"This... is wounderfull"said Vamprah while she watched the mirror.

"Wheeljack to Zardus"said Wheeljack using the comm link "The first 
part of Operation it's done; We will work in the pod and after that; 
vamprah will be ready to go to Maximal city"
